title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 22 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 22 2022
description:
Clay and Buck recap and analyze their hour-long interview with President Trump. Biden from 2020: I'll get tough on Putin. Boris Johnson lifts all covid restrictions in UK. Dr. Marty Makary on natural immunity. The latest on the totalitarian state of Canada. C&B NY affiliate WOR celebrates its 100th birthday. Buck at CPAC this weekend. Florida is now the epicenter of conservatism, home base of the GOP. Beto vs. Abbott in Texas.
